description:
The qualified person should be a team player, very well organized, detail-oriented and capable of working on a timeline.

Requirements:

-advanced understanding of PHP and object-oriented programming (OOP);
-advanced understanding of database development using MySQL;
-good knowledge of any PHP MVC framework like Zend, Symfony or Laravel;
-good knowledge of HTML, CSS, JavaScript (jQuery);
-good knowledge of English and good writing skills;
-basic understanding of code versioning tools, such as git is a plus;

Our Offer:

Attractive salary package and meal tickets.
Holiday bonuses.
Medical services plan.
A-class office building.
Friendly and multicultural working environment.
Opportunity to work in an expanding multinational company.

